data.actual_result: It doesnt actually do anything and wont bring u anywhere
data.expected_result: When opening the quickswitcher in magnificent search glass it should bring you to any server you want
data.short_description: Quick switcher wont let u go to servers when holding down on magnificent glass/search glass [**NOTE**: iPhone 5 and above only (Not iPad!)]
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to any server - hold down on the magnificent glass/search glass - Now it should open the quickswitcher - click on any server icon or dm (if u get any) and notice it wont bring u anywhere (not talking about the channel #'s + names u see)
